# Set the default behavior, in case people don't have core.autocrlf set.
* text=auto

# Declare files with LF line endings

## Isabelle files
*.thy text eol=lf
**/ROOT text eol=lf
**/ROOTS text eol=lf

## Markdown files
*.md text eol=lf

